      "TLS/HTTPS: HMAC is used in the TLS handshake to verify message integrity",
      "Password Hashing: PBKDF2 uses HMAC as its pseudo-random function",
      "Message Queues: Kafka, RabbitMQ use HMAC for message authentication"
    ],

